user_prompt_template.en:
source_lang={source_lang}
target_lang={target_lang}
document_title={document_title}
source_url={source_url}
learning_mode={learning_mode}
difficulty={difficulty}
cloze_max_per_chunk={cloze_max_per_chunk}

You will receive one or more chunks in this format:
chunk_id=chunk_0001
chunk_text=
<chunk text>

Return a JSON array. Each item must be:
{
  "chunk_id": "chunk id",
  "sentence": "a sentence copied from chunk_text",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "text": "phrase copied from sentence",
      "reason": "optional short reason",
      "phrase_types": ["optional taxonomy labels"]
    }
  ]
}

Rules:
1) phrase text must be an exact substring from sentence (no rewrite).
2) Do not output cloze markers, numbering, or hints.
3) Keep high-value learning chunks; skip low-value fillers.
4) If no good phrase exists for a chunk, omit it.
5) Return JSON only.

chunk_text:
{chunk_text}

